.ui.dropdown > .text {
  white-space: nowrap;
  overflow: hidden;
  text-overflow: ellipsis;
  width: 100%;
}
.ui.selection.dropdown,
.ui.selection.dropdown .menu {
  border-radius: 0;
}
.error-message {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  min-height: 200px;
}
.error-message > div {
  width: 50%;
  font-size: 20px;
  color: red;
  white-space: pre-line;
}
.recent-news-preview .recent-news-entries {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(10px, 400px));
  grid-row-gap: 6px;
  grid-column-gap: 6px;
  justify-content: start;
  align-content: center;
  margin-top: 17px;
}
.recent-news-preview .recent-news-viewmore {
  margin-top: 25px;
}
.recent-news-full {
  overflow-y: auto;
  overflow-x: hidden;
  max-height: 100%;
  min-height: 100%;
}
.recent-news-full .recent-news-entries .recent-news-entry-full {
  padding-top: 41px;
  padding-bottom: 41px;
}
.recent-news-full .recent-news-entries .recent-news-entry-full:not(:first-child) {
  border-top: 1px solid #ecf2f8;
}
.recent-news-full .recent-news-entries .recent-news-entry-full p {
  margin-top: 10px;
}
.recent-news-full .recent-news-entries .recent-news-entry-full .read-more-less {
  display: block;
  margin-top: 15px;
  font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  font-style: normal;
  font-weight: normal;
  font-size: 18px;
  line-height: 24px;
  letter-spacing: -0.011em;
  color: #36639f;
}
.recent-news-full .recent-news-viewmore {
  margin-top: 25px;
}
